{"tid":1564503,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]鴨脷洲邨中秋報佳音活動","createTime":"2019-09-12T20:12:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T14:00:52.000Z","uid":300604,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"d1649cf7a67d5adfff476483b68ee98c6c0f45be","tid":1564503,"uid":300604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T20:12:10.000Z","msg":"今晚中秋節 鴨脷洲西邨將會有一個特別活動<br />\n因為尋晚（12/9）迎月夜發生左一件令人震驚嘅事<br />\n有好幾位手足被人從高空投擲鏹水導致受傷留院<br />\n所以街坊希望今晚適逢中秋之夜<br />\n以報佳音嘅形式去光復鴨脷洲西邨<br />\n希望大家可以嚟參與 一齊黎玩下 開心下<br />\n大家都唔希望俾個兇手逍遙法外 係咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎南區街坊聽晚過黎塞爆西邨🤤☺️<br />\n入場請自備觀星筆 黃色自製燈籠仔<br />\n樓主表示聽講今晚月光會幾靚<br />\n應該會有機會迴光反照照到個單位出黎😂<br />\n帶齊玩具喇記得☺️☺️☺️<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HonTejx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHonTejx.jpg&h=86ef0def&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93926db298bc3bb3ec489710131f052d909771cc","tid":1564503,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T20:12:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"48aea4b03279ac13356e368f5e40007170446419","tid":1564503,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T20:16:59.000Z","msg":"[文長][中期檢討]希望大家入黎睇下我地現有既問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1563440/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1563440/page/1</a><br />\n推左幾粒鐘, 正皮升得好慢, 希望大家可以幫我share出去, 我好有信心呢篇文係可以幫助打破現況<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b89ff25b07bf1a535c330e654df7827f4bbc509","tid":1564503,"uid":148016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T20:17:21.000Z","msg":"南區巴絲可以一齊黎玩下喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee55015508d8bdde0c59a2325622eecd82ff676","tid":1564503,"uid":130140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T20:17:57.000Z","msg":"今日起，只推行動post<br />\n其餘一律不推文回覆"},{"pid":"1fc11afc3dec0b55472aa35c0bace128519a4061","tid":1564503,"uid":19476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T23:10:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a39f4baaf39a6e8271dec7a2e0b398c1a3e142ee","tid":1564503,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T23:44:16.000Z","msg":"屌撚死佢地！"},{"pid":"035bb6ba18f7fe1211cacdcbc322f317a3b0afde","tid":1564503,"uid":70679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T23:45:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"92d0fa6eb5f54ff54c24fc9c461d7d8f0fba9edd","tid":1564503,"uid":19476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T23:56:02.000Z","msg":"Psuh"},{"pid":"5819d4d928c82e65bd932193c6541772fb7d0826","tid":1564503,"uid":57153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T00:05:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"320b60164d2f488f529061c820e7276d99e3a796","tid":1564503,"uid":300604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T00:59:36.000Z","msg":"南區街坊出黎一齊玩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b21b082a071b6ad8edc41c6d584d416ed376305f","tid":1564503,"uid":232540,"like":0,"dislike":0